 for prolonged periods, work long hours, and grow older…</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggRTR9XYKM9_text","label":"ggRTR9XYKM9_text","default":"<p>Our discs dry out and shrink, forcing the vertebrae closer together and putting pressure on the nerves.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggWaLe4w3DQ_text","label":"ggWaLe4w3DQ_text","default":"<p>This is the root cause of Sciatica and the leading reason why back pain and stiffness feel never ending.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gg0045cZav__text","label":"gg0045cZav__text","default":"<p>And until you rehydrate your spinal discs, the pain will never truly go away.</p>"}],
